These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, soul, classical
1. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | soul | classical | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Transport   | quad-bike | roller | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, engineer, chef
1. the dancer is on the far left##1
2. the chef is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Job   | dancer | engineer | chef |

 #################################

 
